## 3. Project Setup

```bash
airops init my-tool
cd my-tool
```

This creates:

```
my-tool/
├── tool.py           # Tool implementation (entry point)
├── pyproject.toml    # Package configuration
├── Dockerfile        # Container image for deployment
├── .dockerignore
